				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "If Shar/Shadowheart have told the player about the Spear of Night, they will be given once last reminder to find it before entering the Shadowfell. If the player refuses twice, SH will turn hostile\r\n\r\nCOM: Shadowheart refuses to enter the Shadowfell without the spear. If the player refuses to search for it then Shadowheart leaves the party"
